10542820@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Having metadata about images embedded in TIFF or EXIF files is one way of acquiring additional data about an image.@1@20@@oe@30-11-2008
10542830@unknown@formal@none@1@S@[[Tag (metadata)|Tagging]] pictures with subjects, related emotions, and other descriptive phrases helps Internet users find pictures easily rather than having to search through entire image collections.@1@26@@oe@30-11-2008
