10542890@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Photographers shooting [[RAW image format|Camera RAW]] file formats can use applications such as [[Adobe Bridge]] or Apple Computer's [[Aperture (photography software)|Aperture]] to work with camera metadata for post-processing.@1@28@@oe@30-11-2008
10542900@unknown@formal@none@1@S@=== Audio Metadata ===@1@4@@oe@30-11-2008
